title: 'The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel' Mid-Season Check-In
description:
Joanna Robinson is joined by Mallory Rubin to discuss the big to do with the newest season of 'The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel'. They check in to see what social issues the show attempts to grapple with, meeting historical comedic figures, as well as some missing kids.
Hosts: Joanna Robinson and Mallory Rubin
Senior Producer: Steve Ahlman
